hachu (0.18-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release, including a Makefile.
  * Include a patch to the Makefile for packaging-friendly "install" target.
  * Install xboard confs for Chu and Sho, and theme for Chu; declare that it
    Enhances: xboard (and replace the version that ships an old version of the
    confs).
  * Add menu entries to start Chu and Sho.
  * Declare Recommends: xboard 4.8 as well, as it is still the only
    available way to use the engine.
  * Adjusted extended description.
  * Adjusted instructions for upstream tarball production.
  * Bumped Standards-Version to 3.9.5, no change.

